---
// Landing page for unauthenticated users
---

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-background to-accent/5">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-6xl">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 space-y-6">
      <div class="inline-block">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <svg
            class="size-16 text-primary"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-primary/80 to-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Planer Posiłków
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Inteligentny asystent planowania posiłków z AI, który pomoże Ci
        <span class="text-foreground font-semibold">zaoszczędzić czas</span> i
        <span class="text-foreground font-semibold">stworzyć zdrowy plan żywieniowy</span>
        dla całej rodziny
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center pt-4">
        <a
          href="/register"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-xs hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 px-8 text-base"
        >
          <svg
            class="size-5"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
          Zacznij za darmo
        </a>
        <a
          href="/login"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] border bg-background shadow-xs hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground dark:bg-input/30 dark:border-input dark:hover:bg-input/50 h-11 px-8 text-base"
        >
          Masz już konto? Zaloguj się
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-lg size-12 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg
            class="size-6 text-primary"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Plany tworzone przez AI</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Zaawansowana sztuczna inteligencja generuje spersonalizowane przepisy dopasowane do Twoich potrzeb
          kalorycznych i preferencji kulinarnych
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-lg size-12 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg
            class="size-6 text-primary"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Dla całej rodziny</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Zdefiniuj indywidualne cele kaloryczne dla każdego członka rodziny. AI obliczy idealne porcje w gramach dla
          każdej osoby
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-lg size-12 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg
            class="size-6 text-primary"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Inteligentna lista zakupów</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Automatycznie generowana lista zakupów agreguje składniki z całego planu i kategoryzuje je według działów
          sklepowych
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Jak to działa?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full size-12 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Określ preferencje</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
            Podaj liczbę osób, dni, rodzaj kuchni i cele kaloryczne
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full size-12 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">AI generuje plan</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
            Sztuczna inteligencja tworzy spersonalizowane przepisy
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full size-12 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Zapisz i gotuj</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
            Zapisz plan, wygeneruj listę zakupów i zacznij gotować
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-accent/10 to-primary/10 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-8 md:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Gotowy, aby zacząć?</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Dołącz do tysięcy użytkowników, którzy oszczędzają czas i tworzą zdrowe plany żywieniowe z pomocą AI
        </p>
        <a
          href="/register"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-xs hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 px-8 text-base"
        >
          Stwórz swój pierwszy plan
          <svg
            class="size-5"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

